          <h3>Summary</h3>
          <div class="section-content"><div class="row"><div class="col"><p class="text-justify">Sunspot is a Ruby library for expressive, powerful interaction with the Solr search engine. Sunspot is built on top of the RSolr library, which provides a low-level interface for Solr interaction; Sunspot provides a simple, intuitive, expressive DSL backed by powerful features for indexing objects and searching for them. Sunspot is designed to be easily plugged in to any ORM, or even non-database-backed objects such as the filesystem. Being a collaborator i solve issues, review code and addresses comments.</p></div></div><div class='rvlqplr-placement-046628aa-40bc-4b18-bb04-e20223f91c38'></div></div>
